        "TileImage": "$($repository 07c64264-9fa9-4c4a-a933-802011bee9e6).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47\r\rAfter Hokkaido, a sample of the bioweapon escaped and was sold on the dark web to James King, a prominent actor suspected of having a dark agenda. Intelligence indicates he will receive it tonight, and is planning to use it to secure an award and sabotage his film for profit.\r\rYour mission: eliminate the courier and James King, and recover the bioweapon.\r\rGood hunting, 47",
